Yes. You can&#39;t assume the order of tests, period. Your best bet is to
use something like OrderedTestSuite (http://gsbase.sourceforge.net) to
order the tests as needed.

Also, a little suggestion. Change the setup() code to use this:

     final Context context = new InitialContext();

It&#39;s generally a good practice to store objects in references to the
weakest useful type. It improves your code&#39;s resilience in the face of
change. (Sorry -- I couldn&#39;t resist.)

Good luck.

